/// Prism’s color tabview component, typically used to swich different content of views
/// The Prism does not have any resources such as string tables, so all localized strings have to be given from externel
/// This height of this view does not support resizing. After calling init, the required height of this view is determined, this height can be get from intrinsicContentSize
/// The intrinsic width can be get by intrinsicContentSize. If this view has less width than intrinsic, this view becomes scrollable
/// If the caller of this view does not use auto-layout, please set this view to what intrinsicContentSize returns
/// <h2>Reference</h2>
/// <a href="https://www.figma.com/file/fLGhhzkzA1tlvZOg00to2L/Prism-Desktop-%26-Web-1.0?type=design&node-id=45446-314015&mode=design&t=zQUiAIIoBtaKQKUV-0"><em>Figma</em>:  Tabview Design Specification</a>
